    <h1>B2C Marketing</h1>
    <p class="description">Promoting products and services directly to individual consumers. Built on <strong>short cycles, emotional resonance, and mass channels</strong> like paid social, retail, and search.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
      <div class="meta-author">
        <div class="meta-avatar">AVR</div>
        <div class="meta-author-info">
